display specifications.back:
block-level cannot be contained in inline-level elements in HTML - violation.
CSS can change add this behavior:
	<p><em>example</em></p>
	p {display: inline;}
	em {display: block}

@import directive.back:
note: must be placed before other css rules or it won't work at all

<style type='text/css'>
@import url(style.css);
h1 {color: grey}
</style>
